title: [Orcswold, Grasslands]
description: The field rises in a scrub-covered hillock, the low brush and sparse grass windswept by a stiff breeze from the east.  Several black crows fly near to the ground in the distance, their harsh cries echoing across the barren field.

The field rises in a scrub-covered hillock, the low brush and sparse grass windswept by a stiff breeze from the east.  A lone crow flies near to the ground in the distance, its dark silhouette a shadow against the distant hills.
